            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-03/2023-03-07t021657z_817520670_rc2qoz9jc9ck_rtrmadp_3_china-parliament.jpg?VersionId=Up4e6wVb6Y2t4y0ogjDohlyv5lDvkXl5&amp;itok=rjgwQi2a" title="中国外交部长秦刚星期二（3月7日）在记者会上回答关于中俄关系的提问。（路透社）" alt="中国外交部长秦刚星期二（3月7日）在记者会上回答关于中俄关系的提问。（路透社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-03/2023-03-07t021657z_817520670_rc2qoz9jc9ck_rtrmadp_3_china-parliament.jpg?VersionId=Up4e6wVb6Y2t4y0ogjDohlyv5lDvkXl5&amp;itok=rjgwQi2a" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
